'''''Cairo Station,'''  cyangwa THE IRON GATE'' ( Arabic   ''Bāb al-Ḥadīd'' ), ni filime y’akinywe muri 1958 mu Misiri  iyobowe na Youssef Chahine <ref>https://www.theguardian.com/film/2020/dec/01/cairo-station-egyptian-film-streaming</ref>.  Yinjiye mu marushanwa mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya 8 rya Berlin <ref>https://www.newyorker.com/goings-on-about-town/movies/cairo-station</ref>.  Iyi filime yatoranijwe nkuwinjira mu Misiri muri Filime Nziza Y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 31 bya Osama, . <ref>https://www.newyorker.com/goings-on-about-town/movies/cairo-station</ref> Kuva mu myaka ya za 70, iyi filime yongeye gushimisha n'ibisekuru bishya by'abakunzi ba firime mpuzamahanga<ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/movies/Cairo_Station</ref>. Insanganyamatsiko zerekanwa muri filime zirimo itsinda ry’abakozi bo mu mijyi, ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina, no gukandamiza igitsina<ref>https://mubi.com/films/cairo-station</ref>. 

== Ubusobanuro bwamateka ==
Cairo Station yatangiye bwa mbere mu 1958<ref>https://www.cinemaescapist.com/2020/04/review-cairo-station-egypt-movie/</ref>. Hamwe n'ihirikwa ry'ubwami bwa Misiri mu 1952 , ubushobozi bwa Youssef Chahine bwo gukemura insanganya z'abakozi bo mu mijyi<ref>https://www.showmax.com/eng/movie/628n4ewu-cairo-station</ref>, ihohoterwa rishingiye ku gitsina no gukandamiza igitsina ni ngombwa kubigaragaza kuko byerekana Chahine (n'abayobozi basa) ubushobozi bwo gusunika imbibi za Sinema yo muri Egiputa, ikintu batashoboye gukora mugihe inganda za firime zashyizwe mugihugu mu 1966<ref>https://www.madamasr.com/en/2014/09/13/feature/culture/egypts-cinematic-gems-cairo-station/</ref>. Mu kuvanga injyana ya firime (cyane cyane Neorealism yo mu Butaliyani na Film Noir) Chahine yashoboye kwerekana neza umuryango wa Misiri nkuko byari bimeze mu myaka ya za 1950 kandi abikora abiha Abanyamisiri ndetse n’amahanga kugira ngo basobanure neza ibitekerezo by’imibereho bya Misiri bihinduka, n'indangagaciro nyuma ya revolisiyo isi<ref>https://www.timeout.com/movies/cairo-station</ref>.<ref>https://bunow.com/foreign-film-friday-cairo-station-1958/</ref> 

